xico}}||[[Chinese immigration to Mexico|Chinese Mexican]]||70,000||nil||2008<!---ref name=\"Rodriguez\"/ This isn't a real citation, so I'm adding a citation needed--->{{citation needed|date=June 2017}}\n|-\n|{{flag|Dominican Republic}}||[[Ethnic Chinese in the Dominican Republic]]||50,000|| ||--<ref>{{cite web |url= http://dr1.com/articles/chinese.shtml |title= The Chinese Community and Santo Domingo's Barrio Chino |accessdate= 18 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Costa Rica}}||[[Chinese-Costa Rican]]||45,000||||2011<ref>By Rachel Will\nDate Published: 10/21/2011 [https://web.archive.org/web/20140714113429/http://uschina.usc.edu/article@usct?chinas_stadium_diplomacy_17566.aspx]</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Colombia}}||[[Chinese Colombians]]||25,000|| ||2014<ref>{{cite web |title= Presencia de chinos en Colombia se ha duplicado en ocho a\u00f1os |url= http://agenciadenoticias.unal.edu.co/detalle/article/presencia-de-chinos-en-colombia-se-ha-duplicado-en-ocho-anos.html |publisher= UNIMEDIOS |accessdate=11 February 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Chile}}|| [[Chinese people in Chile]]||20,000|| ||--{{Citation needed|date=November 2010}}\n|-\n|{{flag|Venezuela}}||[[Chinese Venezuelan]]||15,358|| ||2011<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_Venezuelans#cite_note-1 |title=Chinese Venezuelans}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Nicaragua}}||[[Chinese Nicaraguan]]||12,000|| ||--<ref>{{cite news | first= | last= | title=Nicaragua: People groups | publisher= | url =http://www.joshuaproject.net/countries.php?rog3=NU | work =Joshua Project | pages = | accessdate = 2007-03-26 }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Suriname}}||[[Chinese Surinamese|Chinese-Surinamese]]||7,885||1.5%||2012<ref>{{cite web |url=http://unstats.un.org/unsd/demographic/sources/census/2010_PHC/Suriname/SUR-Census2012-vol1.pdf |title=Censusstatistieken 2012 |work=Algemeen Bureau voor de Statistiek in Suriname (General Statistics Bureau of Suriname)  |page=76}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Trinidad and Tobago|name=Trinidad & Tobago}}||[[Chinese Trinidadian and Tobagonian]]||3,800|| ||2000{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}\n|-\n|{{flag|Guyana}}||[[Chinese Guyanese]]||2,722|| ||1921<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rootsweb.ancestry.com/~guycigtr/|title=Chinese in Guyana: Their Roots|website=Rootsweb.ancestry.com|accessdate=18 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Belize}}||[[Ethnic Chinese in Belize]]||1,716|| ||2000<ref>{{cite web |url=http://celade.cepal.org/cgibin/RpWebEngine.exe/PortalAction?&MODE=MAIN&BASE=CPVBLZ2000&MAIN=WebServerMain.inl |title=Redatam: CEPAL/CELADE |publisher=Celade.cepal.org |accessdate=2012-05-07 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120628225923/http://celade.cepal.org/cgibin/RpWebEngine.exe/PortalAction?&MODE=MAIN&BASE=CPVBLZ2000&MAIN=WebServerMain.inl |archivedate=28 June 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n|'''[[Oceania]]'''|| || || ||\n|-\n|{{flag|Australia}}||[[Chinese Australian]]||1,213,903||5.6%||2016<ref>https://quickstats.censusdata.abs.gov.au/census_services/getproduct/census/2016/quickstat/036</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/Lookup/by%20Subject/2071.0~2016~Main%20Features~Cultural%20Diversity%20Data%20Summary~30 | title=Cultural diversity in Australia - 2016 census data summary | publisher=Australian Bureau of Statistics | accessdate=5 July 2019 }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|New Zealand}}||[[Chinese New Zealander]]||231,386||4.9%||2018<ref>https://www.stats.govt.nz/information-releases/2018-census-totals-by-topic-national-highlights</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Fiji}}||[[Chinese in Fiji]]||34,712|| ||2012<ref>[https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/fj.html Fiji], CIA World Factbook, retrieved 23 March 2012</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Samoa}}||[[Chinese in Samoa]]||30,000|| ||--{{Citation needed|date=November 2009}}\n|-\n|{{flag|Papua New Guinea}}||[[Chinese people in Papua New Guinea]]||20,000|| ||2008<ref>{{harvnb|Nelson|2007|p=8}}</ref><ref name=\"Chin 2008 p=118\">{{harvnb|Chin|2008|p=118}}</ref>\